Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.24,0:03:17.21,OP-TC,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}片尾名單過後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.37,0:03:20.00,OP-TC,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}無論等待多久
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.12,0:03:23.37,OP-TC,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}始終不曾上演期待的後續
